3-MULTI-CLASS MULTI

Trying to master 3 classes isn't easy.  But when it is done there isn't 
much you can't do.
#
AC

"AC" is your armor class.  It is a number from -10 to 10, roughly
defined as follows:

  10 Naked person
   0 Badly armored
 -10 Average armored.
 -20 Good armored
 -30 Well armored
 -40 Strongly armored
 -50 For almost all mobs impossible to hit
 -60 Armored battle tank :)

The score command displays your armor class as a number such as 78/10;
this means 78 on a scale from 100 down (i.e., 7.8 on the 10-scale)

See also:  SCORE STAT
#
"ACID BREATH"
Usage           : cast 'acid breath' : cast 59
Damage          : Explained below
Cost            : 100 Mn
Duration        : instant

   This is an Area Affect spell.  The damage basically boils down to 
this:  max of 1d(caster's hp/4) and 10
