ACTIVATE

If you cant enter portal, you need to activate it with special item (key)
which fits this portal. For example:

>activate moongate

#
"ADVANCED MARTIAL ARTS" 

As a ninja progresses and masters Ninjitsu, they learn a multitude of 
deadly kicks, punches, and strikes. Each technique is learned and then 
applicable to the Ninjitsu they already know bestowing bonuses in damage 
to their attacks. These bonuses in damage are only applicable to attacks 
made via Ninjitsu.

SEE NINJITSU, AMA TABLE
#
ALIAS

This is a quite powerful command for those of you who doesn't have a
client program like tintin++.
Make your own aliases.  Shorten down often used and long names.

> alias [SHORT] [REPLACE]  or  alias [load|save|clear]
> alias k kill
> k fido (Will be: kill fido)
> alias z zugerunerweisen
> rescue z
> alias rr recite recall

To remove the alias rr:
> alias rr

You can also define multicommands with alias:
> alias ge get bread bag & eat bread
> alias befriend shake %&smile %&kiss %&french %
> befriend Rigel

See also: TOGGLE SPEEDWALK SAVE
#
