AUCTION GOSSIP CHAT GRAT NEWBIE

These are channels reserved for specific purposes.  Messages on these
channels reach everyone who is monitoring them.  You must be at least 
level two to use these channels.

Don't use colorful language on chat, or you might get muted by an 
Immortal.

auction <string>
newbie <string>
gossip <string>   (Or ,<string>)
chat <string>     (Or .<string>)

> auction short sword -- minimum bid 100k
> gos Hey, is that a short sword on your belt or are you happy to see me?
> grat LEVEL!!!!!!!!
> grat GRATS!!!!!!!
> newbie Where i can find some lvl 5 eq?
> newbie Any lvl 10 who want sapphire ring for free go 1u from temple

auction gossip chat without parameters shows 10 previous messages
was on this channel.

>auc
[Saler]  Pool cue? Hmm have one spared
[Saler]  ok 500k
[Client]  500k
[Saler]  1
[Saler]  2
[Saler]  3... sold temple
[Player]  what was for sale?
[Saler]  Pool cue
[Player]  sold? for 500k?
[Player]  Gotta selfdelete... :(

