#
AUTOASSIST

When you have AUTOASSIST flag toggled on, you authomatically assist 
people from your group. If your group is already fighting when you 
arrived in room, you join battle as well.

See also: TOGGLE ASSIST GROUP

#
BACKSTAB

Rogues only.

Backstab is a way to sneak up on a person and attempt to place your 
dagger in his back, at exactly the point where it does most damage.  A 
successful backstab gives a damage multiplier, depending on level.
The chance of successfully backstabbing a person depends on how well you
have practiced backstab at your guild.  You can always backstab sleeping
people.

See also: CIRCLE
#
BANK WITHDRAW DEPOSIT BALANCE

Commands to take money out of the bank, put money in the bank, or see how
much money you have in the bank.  Can be used at any branch of the First
National Bank of EliteMUD (wherever you see an automatic teller machine).

> deposit 400
> withdraw 1000
> balance

#
BARD

Jack of all trades, master of none. Through their travelling, these
entertainers have picked a variety of skills and spells from other
classes. They know enough of everything to get by.

    You can improve your spells and skills by using the practice
command in Thief Guild.

See also: PRACTICE, GUILD, MIDGAARD

#
BASH

Fighters only.
The success of a bash depends upon how well you are learned. To bash 
someone is to attempt to 'knock' that person over. If you succeed you 
will inflict minor damage, and cause the victim to fall on it's rear.  If 
you miss you loose your balance and fall.

A bash makes you unable to type commands for 2 rounds of violence.

Bash can also be used to bash down closed doors.  This will do a small 
amout of damage to your health.

Fighters See Also : Rescue, Kick
#
"BATTLE TACTICS"

Veterans know the benefict of tactics.  Even for a small group, fighting
strategically is always a benefit.  If you are a leader of a group, you 
will automatically use this skill to aid your party in battle by shouting 
orders to them.
#
BERZERK

Warriors, Cavaliers and Mariners only.
Your adrenaline will flow through your veins and you will hit the foes
harder and faster and meaner until they die OR you do.  Fleeing is out
of the question, and you will also be easier to hit.

> berzerk
