"BLINDNESS"
Usage            : cast 'blindness' <target> : cast 4 <target>
Effect           : -4 Hitroll and +40 AC + target become BLIND.
Cost             : 13 Mn
Duration         : 2 hours

This spell will fail if the target is higher level than the caster
or if the target saves against magic.
