BLUDGEON

A general skill for all classes.  The knowledge of how to use bludgeoning
weapons like hammers, clubs etc.  You will have a greater chance of
hitting your enemy with a bludgeoning weapon.

See also:  PIERCE SLASH STAB CHOP
