CAST
For "magical" people. If you want to throw a spell at someone or 
something.

Example : cast 'burning hands' <player>
   Note that the name of the spell must be enclosed by "'"s.

You can also get the spellnumber and use this format:

cast SPELLNR <TARGET>
> cast 26 fido -> cast 'fireball' fido -> BARBEQUE PARTY

