"CLAN TUTORIAL" CLAN
 
Welcome to EliteMud Clan Code Tutorial.
 
For more info on certain topics, type the following:
CLAN HELP <TOPIC>  or   HELP CLAN <TOPIC>
 
Choose one of the following topics:
        GENERAL         FOUNDATION      RULES           COMMANDS
        DEITY           HOUSE           RANKS           PROBATION
        MOB             EQ              SHOPKEEPER
#
"CLAN GENERAL"

Elite clans are based on membership and ranks.  You can only be a 
member of one clan (at a time).  What you do for the clan and what 
the clan requires from you is totally dependent on the rules of the 
clan and who is leading it.  To apply to join a clan, you have to be 
level 10 or greater.  Each clan may have a different minimum level 
for membership, so check the clan's info.

#
"CLAN FOUNDATION" 

To be able to found and run a clan, certain criteria must be 
fulfilled from you.  In general, you should be an experienced player 
and know EliteMud fairly well.  You must be able and willing to take
responsibility for what you and your members do and practice as a 
clan.  You must know the clan rules, and follow them.  If interested, 
please contact the immortal in charge of clans to start the application 
process.

The details of what you will need on the application include:
        1.  An original theme. <must be a medieval or fantasy theme,
            one which will not clash with the theming of Elite.>
        2.  A name and color scheme for your clan.
        3.  The 20 names of the characters wishing to form the clan
            <Multis do not count in the orginal 20.  An immortal member 
            is highly recommended, but is not required.>
        4.  A listing of the proposed clan ranks and start up 
            officers.
        5.  A clan info as it would be listed if the clan was accepted.
        6.  A clan symbol

A fee of 200M gold and 5 QPs will be charged if your clan gets accepted.  Be 
sure to have this readily available.

For details on what your fee will entitle you to:
See Also:  CLAN HOUSE

#
"CLAN RULES"

These rules are subject to change.  All changes will be posted on the 
main clan board, so be sure to check it ever now and then.

* Clans may not in any way contribute to an anti-social behaviour.
* Within the clan, the clan rules are followed, assuming they do 
  follow the general EliteMud policies. ( use: POLICY command )
* The clan leader(s) are responsible for all members.  Members who 
  break the clan rules should be dealt with accordingly by the 
  leaders of that clan.

#
"CLAN COMMANDS"

By using the command CLAN, you will get a list of the clan 
subcommands you can use.  As you raise in ranks in your clan, you
will get more.

Short descriptions of what some subcommands do:
        APPLY   You apply for membership with this clan.
                > clan apply <clan vnum>
        INFO    Info about the clans.  Their vnums, rules, stats
                and more.
                > clan info
                > clan info <clan vnum>
        SYMBOL  Shows clan symbol.
                > clan symbol <clan vnum>
        HELP    Help on clan system.
        TITLE   Will toggle the display of your clan name and rank in 
                the who list.
        RESIGN  You will leave you clan unconditionally.  If you are 
                not happy with your clan, use this command.
        ENLIST  Enrolls a character into your clan.
                >clan enlist <character>
        RAISE   Advance a clan member to the next higher clan level.
                >clan raise <character>
        DEMOTE  Lower a clan member to the next lower clan level.
        EXPEL   Remove a clan member from your clan.
        TELL    The clan's communication channel.
                > ct "<message>"
                or, for ctell only for ppl with your clan lvl or 
                above:
                >ct #<clan level> <message>
                Without parameters it show a last 10 messages you
                heard on ctell:
                >ct
                [Member (2)] Hi clan
                [Leader (2)] Hi Member :)
                [Leader (5)] I think he deserved to be promoted
                [Remort (5)] No, I think hes a moron.
                [Immo   (9)] Hey Leader, leave this up to me.
         WHO    Lists the clan members currently in the game.
         ROSTER Shows list of members in clan you ask about.
                >clan roster <clan vnum>
         POWER  Shows the activity of all the clans during that 
                particular reboot period.

#
"CLAN DEITY"

A immortal may choose to be your clan 'deity', or immortal leader.
He/She will be the voice of your clan in the immortal realm.  The 
immortal may only be part of discipliniary action or answer 
questions.  He/she is to see that the clan rules and EliteMUD policy 
are followed.  Immorts MAY NOT:
        retrieve corpses
        load equipment
        help in mob killing
        or in any other way break the general Imm rules.

#
"CLAN HOUSE"

Costs of renovations or new construction:
   #cBasic clan house                               200M/5QPs#N
       #c*#N 10 Rooms (1 Donation room, 1 Regen room)
       #c*#N Clan Guard, Clan Board
       
   #cClan Rewrite (Name+info+ranks changes)         100M

   #cClan info/rank/commands#N                        3M each

   #cExtra rooms                                 Price per room#N
       11-30                                         10M
       31-50                                         15M
       51-75                                         20M
       76-99                                         30M
       
   #cRoom changes#N                                   5M

   #cSpecial Flags                               Price per flag#N
       silent, private, no_mob                      FREE
       no_quit, no_summon                            10M
       regen, lawfull, pkok, no_drop                 20M

   #cSpecial Objects                             Price per obj#N
       Container                                     10M
       Statue                                        15M
       Guard (can set for specific clanlevels)       20M
       Board                                         25M
       ATM                                           25M
       Fountain                                      25M
          #c*#N Custom Fountain                          35M

   #cSpecial Mobs                                Price per mob#N
       Mob                                           30M
       Mob with actions                              35M
       Shopkeeper w/ 3 items                         40M
          #c*#N Additional items                       5M each

  #c*#N Only one donation room per clan.

For details on clan mob restrictions:
