CLIMB

There are many hills and mountains in the world that keeps most 
adventurers away.  This skill will let you explore some of these 
mountains.
#
COLORS

In ELITE there is a color system implemented, which allows you to use 
colors in your titles/messages etc.

      Color for foreground shall be defined by
            ##<color-letter>, where letter is:

 #r##r - red        #b##b - blue      #y##y - yellow  #g##g - green
 #c##c - cyan       #m##m - magenta   #w##w - white   #W##W and #N##N - normal

 #R##R - dark red  #B##B - dark blue    #Y##Y - dark yellow #G##G - dark green
 #C##C - dark cyan #M##M - dark magenta #e##e - dark grey#N

     for ex: "##Ctest##rtest##N." looks as "#Ctest#rtest#N."

      Important: Do not forget ##N in end of colored text.

Colors for background are defined by
  ##:<color_letter>.

                      Examples:

 ##:r##y  - #:r#y yellow on red#N

 ##N returns background color to normal as well as foreground.


WARNING: on some terminals colors worked incorrectly so please be aware:
when using background colors your text can screw up terminals of other
players.

#
"COLOR SPRAY"
Usage           : cast 'color spray' <victim> : cast 10 <victim>
Damage          : 2d12 + level + level/2 (max of 20)
Cost            : 13 Mn
Duration        : instant
