DEMONS

Demons are the manifestion of all that is evil in the world of elite.
Feeding on the souls of the damned, they lack the mortal need for
sustenance.  Living their entire lives shrouded in darkness, they remain
unhampered by the mortal need for light to see.  Only those who prove 
their vileness and cruelty can join the demons in their mission to defile 
purity and goodness.  Many are rejected, and are doomed to spend their 
lives hampered by the restraints of goodness. 

