"DRAIN LIFE"
Usage           : cast 'drain life' victim : cast 100 <victim>
Damage          : (1d8 + 8) * (level / 5)
Cost            : 45 Mn
Duration        : instant

You also regain (damage / 4) (max of 75) hitpoints.
