If you feel benevolent, you may give some stuff to someone in need.

give <object> <victim>
give <number> coins <victim>

> give all Helm
> give bread Sarastro
> give all.recall fido
> give 2 coins Mithrandir
#
GNOME

Gnomes are a race of good-natured creatures that originated in the
forests east of Midgaard.  They look much like dwarves, but are not
quite as stocky.  Gnomes generally have light colored hair and eyes
and a rosy complexion.  They are long-lived and sturdy folk.  Gnomes
are intelligent, but they tend to focus their attentions on unsolvable
problems.  Gnome scientists are common, but none ever seem to become
famous!
#
GRAB HOLD

For getting a good grip on something; a torch, for example. Note that you
can both hold a weapon and wield one at the same time.

> hold torch
> grab stone

See also: WEAR, WIELD, EQUIPMENT, REMOVE EQUIPMENT
