Heal also removes blindness.
#
HIDE

Rogues Only.

When you type hide there is a chance that you hide in the room. If hidden
you can only be "sensed" by the "sense life" spell. Even if sensed your
identity will remain hidden. Hide is broken by pressing return, 
regardless of wherther you typed a command or not.

Example:

> hide
Ok.
>  (you wait for ex. 5 mins and remain hidden for 5 mins)

>  (You pressed enter and no longer hide)

See Also : SNEAK
#
"HOLY WRATH"
Usage         : cast 'holy wrath' : cast 110
Cost          : 80 Mn
Duration      : 4 hrs.
Effect        : This spell allows the holy warrior class of the paladin 
                to call down the wrath of their gods to slay their 
                opponents.  The paladin is gifted with some additional 
                hitroll based upon their level.
                It imbues a +1 hitroll for every 10 levels after level 20.
#
HUMAN

Humans are a large race of creatures with adequate strength and
intelligence, enabling them to learn a variety of skills and trades.
Humans get along pretty well with most other races, but have a they
have a tendency to believe that they are superior to all of them.
Their appearance varies greatly depending on their region of origin.
The humans from the southern seas tend to have dark hair and eyes,
while those hailing from north of Midgaard are usually more fair.
Humans are not particularly long-lived, but they are capable of
achieving a great deal in their short lives.
#
HUNT

Why bother to bring food along.  Just flush out a rabbit and eat new-
roasted rabbit.

> hunt

See also:  TRACK
