#
IMMORTALS

Players/Characters may apply for an immortal character when the need is
posted.  Having an immortal is a privilege, NOT a right.  Abuse of your
immortal powers could result in punishment or deletion.  It is best to
have some amount of experience of EliteMUD when applying for an immortal.

You may also inquire about aquiring an immortal on the test site if you
are interesting in zone building or player testing.

