INFO NEWS CREDITS VERSION MOTD

These commands show you important information about EliteMUD.  It is a 
good idea to read them every once in a while.

info     - useful information about recent code updates   
news     - latest changes to the code and areas
policy   - policies on topics like playerkilling
credits  - the people who made EliteMUD possible!
version  - displays the current EliteMUD version number
motd     - shows the loginscreen with important messages

For those who have speedwalk on, type NEWS in capital letters!
