KNIGHT

Knights live by their code of honour. As skilled and as fearless as
warriors in battle, these fighters have also been blessed with minor
healing powers as a reward for their virtue.

    You can improve your spells and skills by using the practice
command in Warrior Guild.

See also: PRACTICE, GUILD, MIDGAARD

