LEVEL

This is the basic meassure of your power. You start playing at level 1
and by killing mobs and gaining experience you raise in level. At level
109 you can choose between remorting and immorting. If you are more than
one class, for example Thief/Cleric, you need to level all of your 
classes.

See Also: EXPERIENCE, REMORT, IMMORTALS, STATS, SCORE, LEVELS
