Effect           : AC -40
Cost             : 40 Mn
Duration         : 25 hrs

Only possible to use on yourself.
#
NINJA

The Ninja class studies the discipline of murder and deception. They are 
reasonably trained in the arts of a thief and in weapons but work best 
using few weapons or none at all. Many times a ninja seems outclassed 
they will drop their weapons, smile at their opponents and calmly engage 
them in their own particular breed of combat. Ninja study unarmed combat 
during their lives, how to take life without leaving a mark on an enemy, 
and develop their own forms of attack with higher training.
#
NINJITSU

Ninjitsu is the study of bare-handed attacks, a ninja may elect to use no 
weapons and strike an opponent with their body. By fighting in this 
manner they negate all bonuses to damage except those incurred by their 
striking styles.

SEE ADVANCED MARTIAL ARTS, AMA TABLE
#
NORTH SOUTH EAST WEST UP DOWN

To walk (or ride if mounted) in a given direction.
#
NOSUMMON

Back in the time when there was no laws, players were allowed to kill
eachother. In that time evil people used "summon" to summon others
to dangerous places. The Immortals decided that they had to do something
to protect the innocent, so they created summon protection, which
is turned on by default. Nowadays it is not possible to kill other
players exept in PK-OK zones and you cannot summon another person into
a PK-OK zone. To allow other players to summon you, type "tog summon".

> tog summon

See Also: TOGGLE
#
NOTELL

Use TOGGLE TELL if you wish to prevent other players from using "tell" to
communicate with you.  (notell) will appear after your name in the WHO
list if you have notell on.

See also: FLAGS TELL WHO TOGGLE REPLY
#
OEDIT

An oedit is a piece of equipment that has been magically altered
by an immortal to have a unique name and description. You may come
across oedits during quests, or being used by some older players.
At one time, it was possible to purchase a permanent oedit for a cost
of 1 quest point, but this is no longer the case.

#
OFFER RENT

There is no renting on ELiteMUD, you simply save and quit.
