Used for ordering pets and charmed people to do your evil bidding.  You
can order everyone under your command with "order followers".

order <character> <command>
order followers <command>

> order puppy kiss IO
> order cityguard sleep

See also:  CHARM
#
PALADIN

Paladins are the soldiers of their church. They have taken oath to turn
the world's faithless to the true religion. They are proficient in both
combat skills and healing magics.

    You can improve your spells and skills by using the practice
command in Cleric Guild.

See also: PRACTICE, GUILD, MIDGAARD
#
PARRY PARRYING

This skill enables you to parry enemy attacks.  This means that you
will not get hit as much during battle.
