QUEST

Quests are immortal-run special events. There is no set format for
quests, although in general they involve some amount of role-playing,
problem solving or combat against unusual opponents. The best way
to join in a quest is to interact with mobs who appear to be talking
with players - then follow hints and instructions. Sometimes quests
will be announced in advance on the Quest Board in the library
(swwnnnw).

Very often, as a reward for successful participation in a quest you
will be awarded Quest Points. These will show in a separate line
in your score. When you have enough points, you can use them to
purchase special quest items from the quest shopkeeper in the library.

#
QSAY

To tell something to everyone on the current Quest.
