"STAT STATS"

Will display your statistics. This includes your age and leve, your
armour class, hitroll, damroll and resistances, and also your
characteristics like strength, intelligence, wisdom, dexterity, 
constitution and charisma. It also lists any skills or spells that
are currently active.
#
