"SUMMON"
Usage          : cast 'summon' <victim> : cast 40 <victim>
Duration       : Instant
Cost           : 45 Mn
Save           : Save vs. Magic

When cast, this spell will transport another player or mobile to
the caster. Mobiles will get a saving throw.
#
SWEEPER

Every day, the mud loads about thirty thousand objects. If they
were just left lying around, then very quickly the mud would be
full of junk.

To prevent this, when a zone resets, a SWEEPER goes through each
room in the zone, and clears away any discarded objects. This is
why it is dangerous to leave objects lying around on the ground - 
they might get cleared up by mistake!

To avoid losing items, NEVER drop them in game zones. The only safe
places to drop items are inside your clanhouse, or in the donation
room in Midgaard.

#
SWIM

With this skill, you can swim across lakes, rivers and other shallow 
waters.
#
"TELEPORT"
Usage          : cast 'teleport' : cast 2
Cost           : 50 Mn
Duration       : Instant

When cast, this spell will randomly transport the caster to another
room. Use with caution, since you can teleport into really dangerous
places.
