"UNFAIR FIGHT"

You are familiar with all the tricks to make you the winner of a fight.  
Some sand in the eyes.  A well placed kick in the groins.  A bite on his 
arm.  This skill is automatical and will be used when opportunity arises. 
It will not however do any damage to the opponent.
